-- Cross-tenant verification
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- After deploying these policies, run the 7-step protocol from
-- docs/runtime/cross-tenant-rls-verification.md to confirm isolation.
-- Expected output: every cross-tenant probe (anon + wrong-tenant auth +
-- service_role scope) returns 0 rows OR permission-denied.
